  "description": "A hymn heard from underwater. Very low filter cutoff with gentle resonance creates the acoustic effect of water absorption — high frequencies vanish, leaving only the warm body of the voice. Heavy portamento makes pitch transitions liquid. Stage at maximum for the immense reverb of open ocean.",
